name: Seto Danu
review: This is actually an interesting place to visit because basically this is an island in the meddle of huge river.  in the past, you can reach this place by using sky train that cross the entire one side of the river for a hill from afar. Unfortunately maybe it is true that it is a bit lack or general service and maybe the location of this destination is far from main city so people need to plan if they just want to visit this one. either way, surrounding this island, you can find other historical palace as well. So, this island can be a good bonus to explore this area.
